public enum RevocationReason extends Enum<RevocationReason> implements UriBasedEnum
This enum is used to get String value of CRLReason The CRLReason enumeration.

  unspecified             (0),
  keyCompromise           (1),

  cessationOfOperation    (5),
  certificateHold         (6),

  aACompromise           (10)
 }
